<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/style.css">
  <title>{{title}} | ABROLLER.TECH</title>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <a href="/">ABROLLER.TECH</a>
  </header>
  <main>
    <article itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting">
        <h1 itemprop="headline">{{title}}</h1>

        <p><time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="{{item.date | datetimeDate}}">{{date | dateJp}}</time></p>

        <div itemprop="articleBody">
          {{ content | safe }}
        </div>

        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
          <h2>この記事を書いた人</h2>
          <dl>
            <dt>名前</dt>
            <dd itemprop="name">{{author.name}}</dd>
            <dt>Twitter</dt>
            <dd>
              <a href="https://twitter.com/{{author.twitter}}">
                {{author.twitter}}
                <meta itemprop="url" content="https://twitter.com/{{author.twitter}}">
              </a>
            </dd>
          </dl>

          <p itemprop="description">{{author.description}}</p>
        </footer>
    </article>
  </main>

  <footer>
    (c) 腹筋ローラーの力を信じろ
  </footer>
</body>
</html>